  <brief_title>TAP Block With Magnesium Sulfate Added to Local Anesthetic in Abdominal Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Magnesium Sulfate Added to Local Anesthetic in TAP Block for Postoperative Analgesia Following Total Abdominal Hysterectomy.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
