    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  weight: 50- 85 kg.

          -  ASA score: I-III

          -  scheduled for total abdominal hysterectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of relevant drug allergy.

          -  coagulation disorders.

          -  opioid dependence.

          -  sepsis.

          -  psychiatric illnesses that would interfere with perception and assessment of pain.
